history.content: If I, a senior EECS major, have already completed 5 or more CS/EECS Upper Division courses for a letter grade prior to this semester, one of which fulfills the design requirement and each of which is 4 units, am I allowed to P/NP any future CS Upper Division courses I take, either this semester or the next, provided the total number of units I take P/NP is less than 1/3rd of the total number of units I've taken at the time of graduation?
history.subject: EECS UD P/NP policy
